.Sh NAME
.Nm grapheme_len
.Nd determine grapheme cluster length
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In grapheme.h
.Ft size_t
.Fn grapheme_len "const char *"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
returns the length (in bytes) of the grapheme cluster beginning at
the provided char-address.
.Sh EXAMPLES
.Bd -literal
